Entries.default: "We hear Ernezzo is dead. We shall keep your secret."
"We hear many secrets whispered in this place."
"Do you hear? The drip-drip-drip of water on ancient bones, ancient stones."
"Some say an entire city hides under this one. How many secrets it must hold!"
"You smell of wild, wanton lands, filled with things to discover."
"You smell of forbidding, frozen lands with secrets shrouded in ice."
"I smell on you the rot of fallen empires. Old Vailia, yes?"
